## ‚ö†Ô∏è **Potential Challenges & Mitigations**

| Challenge                                 | Mitigation                                          |
| ----------------------------------------- | --------------------------------------------------- |
| **Name matching** (Sarah ‚Üí sarah@company) | Use Atlassian user directory + fuzzy matching       |
| **Ambiguous deadlines** ("by next week")  | Default to reasonable dates + allow editing         |
| **Complex conversations**                 | Start with simple pattern matching, enhance with AI |
| **Privacy concerns**                      | Clear data handling policy, optional transcription  |

